(power_pad, time).explanation: Power consumption of I/O pads does not directly influence processor execution timing, as pad power is primarily related to interface operations rather than computational performance;

(power_pad, area_net_area).explanation: I/O pad power consumption and interconnect net area are independent design metrics that do not directly influence each other in processor architecture;

(power_pad, area_cell_area).explanation: Power consumption of I/O pads and the physical area of logic cells are separate design parameters that do not have a direct causal relationship;
